{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"49beb57d-774e-42b5-b0b3-4137b81e4252","agentId":"a812a593d484a9d3f","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Fix error handling issues in `/root/jake_desktop/static/js/financeiro.js`. Use Grep to find each function before editing.\n\n## Fixes Needed\n\n### Fix 1: carregarDados() — check HTTP status\n\nGrep for `carregarDados` to find the function. Read it (~20 lines).\n\nIn the Promise.all fetch calls, add `r.ok` check:\n\nChange:\n```javascript\nfetch('/api/financeiro/transacoes').then(function(r){ return r.json(); }),\nfetch('/api/financeiro/raiox').then(function(r){ return r.json(); })\n```\n\nTo:\n```javascript\nfetch('/api/financeiro/transacoes').then(function(r){ if(!r.ok) throw new Error('HTTP '+r.status); return r.json(); }),\nfetch('/api/financeiro/raiox').then(function(r){ if(!r.ok) throw new Error('HTTP '+r.status); return r.json(); })\n```\n\n### Fix 2: editarTransacao() — add error feedback\n\nGrep for `editarTransacao` to find the function. Read it.\n\nThe fetch for PUT currently has only `.catch()`. Add a `.then()` to check `r.ok` and log the error if HTTP fails:\n\nChange the fetch chain from:\n```javascript\n    fetch('/api/financeiro/transacoes/' + id, {\n      method: 'PUT',\n      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n      body: JSON.stringify(campos)\n    }).catch(function(e) { console.error('Erro ao editar transação:', e); });\n```\n\nTo:\n```javascript\n    fetch('/api/financeiro/transacoes/' + id, {\n      method: 'PUT',\n      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n      body: JSON.stringify(campos)\n    }).then(function(r){ if(!r.ok) console.error('Erro ao editar transação: HTTP '+r.status); })\n      .catch(function(e) { console.error('Erro ao editar transação:', e); });\n```\n\n### Fix 3: deletarTransacao() — add error feedback\n\nSame pattern as Fix 2. Find `deletarTransacao`, add `.then()`:\n\n```javascript\n    fetch('/api/financeiro/transacoes/' + id, { method: 'DELETE' })\n      .then(function(r){ if(!r.ok) console.error('Erro ao deletar transação: HTTP '+r.status); })\n      .catch(function(e) { console.error('Erro ao deletar transação:', e); });\n```\n\n## After Fixes\n\nGrep to verify carregarDados has the `r.ok` checks:\n```bash\ngrep -n \"r.ok\" /root/jake_desktop/static/js/financeiro.js\n```\n\nThen commit:\n```bash\ncd /root && git add jake_desktop/static/js/financeiro.js\ngit commit -m \"fix: validar HTTP status nas chamadas fetch do financeiro.js\"\n```\n\nReport DONE when complete."},"uuid":"0522dcbe-b2b4-4b5f-a23d-ad73de193163","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:43:12.723Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/root","sessionId":"cf3d736a-f9d4-4db4-8829-2b4c6fa7cf54","version":"2.1.80","gitBranch":"main","slug":"humming-orbiting-lecun"}
